---
title: Breaded Ranch Chicken Thighs with Potato Coins and Green Beans
description: Everyone's favourite dip – ranch – plays double duty in this satisfying supper! It adds zing to a side of potatoes, plus we've also snuck some under the breadcrumb topping for your chicken!
